nd services also vary around the world insurance and financial products and services are provided by licensed members of the zurich insurance group zurich not all products or services listed are available in all jurisdictions or to all customers please contact your local zurich office for details about the relevant products and services in your country no warranties or guarantees are being made by zurich based on statements on this website find claim services in your country i’m in please select i’m please select i need please select go to your local zurich company information about zurich  zurich insurance zurich insurance group find us newsletter contact us proposal to elect michel m liès as chairman in board of directors will propose the election of michel m liès as chairman at the agm  upon his election he would succeed tom de swaanread news release herestrong performance and a new strategy annual report and annual review now availableread moreeconomic risks an opportunity for reformdiscover the fresh insightscarbon emission and energy consumption targets reachedwe are already exceeding current carbon emission and energy consumption targets and sets new ambitious targets to be achieved by read morewhich zurich golf ambassador loves golf mostwatch the interviews about us zurich insurance group a global insurer zurich operates globally and locally according to our customers’ needs the zurich strategy zurich is positioning for the future by enhancing delivery to its customers corporate governance structure of zurich the organization of our board and our management is structured to support both bodies in fulfilling their commitment to deliver zurich contact information zurich contacts for general inquiries media investors and share register services five reasons to work for zurich youre interested in working in a dynamic challenging environment for a company that recognizes and rewards your creativity initiative and contributions excellent youre in the right place t